'''Ruth Mompati''' (14 Loetse 1925 - 12 Mots'eanong 2015) e ne e le ralipolotiki oa [[Aforika Borwa]] ebile e le e mong oa baetapele ba Basali ba Mmesa ka la 9 Phato 1956.<ref name=":0">http://www.sahistory.org.za/people/ruth-mompati</ref>

== Tsa bonyaneng le thuto ==
Ruth Mompati o tshotshwe ko bontlheng jwa le fatshe jwa [[Bokone Bophirima]]. Ka morago gwa go fetsa dithuto tsa gagwe tsa mophato wa borataro, a berekela lelwapa la batho ba basweu morago ga nako a tsena Tygerkloof Terachers Training College.<ref>Ruth, Mompati (1970). http://www.sadet.co.za/docs/RTD/stories/Stories%20-%20Ruth%20Mompati.pdf . South African democracy education trust: Tsehai publisher and distributors. p. 307.</ref><ref>Turok, Karina. 2006. https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/70536542 Orford, Margie. Cape Town: Double Storey. p. 50. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number  https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-77013-043-8<nowiki/>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OCLC<nowiki/>https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/70536542</ref>

== Tsa Tiro ==
Go tswa 1953 go fitlha 1961 odirile mmereko jwa motlanyi adirela [[Nelson Mandela]] le Oliver Tambo ko di ofising tsa bona tsa molao ko [[Johannesburg]].<ref name=":1">[http://publishing.cdlib.org/ucpressebooks/view?docId=ft4p3006kc&chunk.id=d0e4706&toc.depth=1&brand=ucpress http://publishing.cdlib.org/ucpressebooks/view?docId=ft4p3006kc&chunk.id=d0e4706&toc.depth=1&brand=ucpress''cdlib.org''.]</ref> A nna leloko la mokgatlho jwa [[African National Congress]] ka 1954 a be a kgethiwa gonna leloko la komiti jwa baakamedi ba mokgatlho jwa basadi mo setshabeng jwa [[African National Congress]]. <ref name=":0" />  

A tlhopiwa go nna leloko la palamente ka ditlhopo tsa ntlha tsa temokrasi tsa [[Aforika Borwa]] ka ngwaga wa 1994, a tlhomiwa moemedi wa [[Aforika Borwa]] ko Switzerland go tloga ka 1996 fo fitlha 2000, a nna matoropo wa Vryburg morago gwa go boa ko Switzerland, mme a bereka e le mookame jwa leloko jwa Umkhonto we Sizwe Veteran's Association.<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />  

== Tsa Loso ==
